msgstr ""
"Tha Grylli a’ toirt a-steach stiùireadh togte air feadh an aplacaid gus do "
"chuideachadh le bhith a’ rèiteachadh agus a’ riaghladh na stèisein agad."

#: /home/osuhickeys/Documents/Docker/grylli/app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Tha an duilleag seo a’ toirt sealladh farsaing air prìomh fheartan agus "
"ceanglaichean dìreach far an urrainnear an riaghladh."

